Barriers that you might see.

00:58:01.480 --> 00:58:05.890
How you engage with the team
and the organization around you.

00:58:05.890 --> 00:58:08.520
And some challenges
that you might see,

00:58:08.520 --> 00:58:11.760
and how you've gotten over them
or if they still exist for you.

00:58:11.760 --> 00:58:14.510
So I'd love to continue that
conversation with you, too,

00:58:14.510 --> 00:58:15.350
